主要翻译
 
conditioning n (psychology: behaviour modification)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 条件反射 tiáo jiàn fǎn shè TC Traditional Chinese 條件反射  (心理学)
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 条件反射作用 tiáo jiàn fǎn shè ，tiáo jiàn fǎn shè zuò yòng 
 -- Conditioning causes them to expect food when they hear a bell.
 
conditioning adj (product: that conditions)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 护理的 hù lǐ de TC Traditional Chinese 醫務助理的  
 -- This conditioning mask will make your skin more radiant.

主要翻译
 
condition n (state)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 状况 zhuàng kuàng TC Traditional Chinese 狀況  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 状态 zhuàng kuàng，zhuàng tài TC Traditional Chinese 狀態 
 -- This house is in terrible condition.  It needs a lot of work.
 -- 这栋房子的状况很差，需要大修。
 
condition n (beings: general state)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese （人类的）处境 rén lèi de chǔ jìng  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 生存状态 rén lèi de chǔ jìng，shēng cún zhuàng tài 
 -- Philosophers consider the human condition.
 -- 哲学家思考人类的处境。
 
condition n (medicine: health)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 状况 zhuàng kuàng TC Traditional Chinese 狀況  (健康状况)
 -- The cancer patient is in stable condition.
 -- 该癌症病人状况稳定。
 
condition n (requirement)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 前提条件 qián tí tiáo jiàn TC Traditional Chinese 前提條件  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 必要条件 qián tí tiáo jiàn，bì yào tiáo jiàn TC Traditional Chinese 必要條件 
 -- I will do it - on one condition.
 -- A drug test is a condition of employment here.
 -- 我会做的——不过有一个前提条件。
 -- 药物检测是这里聘用员工的必要条件。
 
condition n (illness)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 健康问题 jiàn kāng wèn tí TC Traditional Chinese 健康問題  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 疾病 jiàn kāng wèn tí，jí bìng TC Traditional Chinese 疾病 
 -- He has a heart condition.
 -- 他有心脏疾病。
 
conditions npl (environment)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 环境 huán jìng TC Traditional Chinese 環境  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 条件 huán jìng，tiáo jiàn TC Traditional Chinese 條件 
 -- Fishermen work in difficult conditions.
 -- 渔夫们在恶劣的条件下劳作。
 
condition [sb] # vtr (brainwash, affect behaviour)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 使适应 shǐ shì yìng TC Traditional Chinese 使適應  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 使有准备 shǐ shì yìng ，shǐ yǒu zhǔn bèi 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 使习惯于 shǐ shì yìng ，shǐ xí guàn yú 
 -- Politicians are conditioning the people to accept the policy.
 -- 政客们在让人们做好心理准备，好接受这一政策。
 
condition [sth] # vtr (body, muscles)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 使（身体、肌肉等）适应于… shǐ shēn tǐ jī ròu děng shì yìng yú  
 -- He is conditioning his body for the race.
 -- 他正在进行调整，使自己的身体适应比赛。
 
condition [sth] vtr (hair: apply conditioner)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 给（头发）涂护发素  
 -- I always condition my hair after washing.
 -- 我在洗头后总会给头发涂护发素。

复合形式：  conditioning  |  condition
 
air conditioning n (system: cools the air)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 空调 kōng tiáo  
 -- I only turn on the air conditioning on the hottest days.
 
air conditioning, air-conditioning n as adj (system: for cooling air)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 空调的  
 -- The air-conditioning system has broken down.
 
air conditioning unit n (device: cools the air)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 空调装置 kōng tiáo zhuāng zhì TC Traditional Chinese 空調裝置  
 -- The repairman will arrive between 1-4pm today to fix your air conditioning unit.

